author: Alicia Victoria Lozano
title: California fast-tracks plans to house homeless residents amid COVID-19 outbreak
description: "We have a moral and ethical responsibility to do our part,” said Los Angeles County Supervisor Hilda L. Solis.
content:
LOS ANGELES The hotel guests checked in one by one, handing their belongings to a uniformed employee waiting with a luggage cart.
